data.description: BEAUTIFUL move in ready home on an oversized lot in a cul-de-sac, located in the desirable neighborhood of Riverstone Ranch. Tons of UPGRADES! Upon entry you are greeted by an elegant formal dining room where the owner added shiplap on the ceilings, WOW!  After passing through the entryway you come to a stunning family room featuring a soaring HIGH ceiling, tile floors, a stone fireplace & floor to ceiling windows that shower the space in natural light! Gorgeous island kitchen equipped with granite countertops, tile floors/backsplash, stainless steel appliances & ample storage space! Master suite includes Bay windows, shiplap wall with a large bathroom, a walk-in closet, a garden soaking tub & a tiled shower!  Second floor features a massive Gameroom, private doors and balcony views. Backyard is oversized and perfect for a future pool and outdoor kitchen. Community amenities include lakes, pool, recreation center and trails. Do not miss out on this amazing opportunity!
